msgid "Troubled Inmate"
msgstr "Detenuto Turbato"

msgctxt "440"
msgid "Talk_No"
msgstr "Talk_No"

msgctxt "72_Troubled Inmate"
msgid ""
"This is too much. I've been dreaming of gourmet dinners every night. Then I "
"wake up to whatever this is."
msgstr ""
"È troppo. Mi sogno cene da gourmet tutte le notti. Poi mi sveglio e mi "
"ritrovo questo schifo."

msgctxt "84_Troubled Inmate"
msgid "Maybe I'll get used to it."
msgstr "Magari mi ci abituerò."
